 class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時放假揸車入去會所玩<br />\n都係老母屋企舒服！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8085467036924b80f1bc609c0d149fc9b5810386","tid":688632,"uid":52090,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T15:06:59.000Z","msg":"唔信咁多人冇路過黃大仙，<br />\n只計MTR你搭觀塘都好大機會經過，<br />\n18區嘅黃大仙唔係得個廟仔<br />\n龍翔道同大老山都係黃大仙區入面<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n黃大仙區位於九龍半島東面，北方背靠獅子山、大老山及慈雲山，東臨飛鵝山，包括竹園、黃大仙、牛池灣、鑽石山、慈雲山、斧山、樂富、橫頭磡、新蒲崗等地方，因此本區亦成全香港唯一無海岸線的行政區。<br />\n<br />\n啟德明渠源自慈雲山，至蒲崗村道成為明渠，沿彩虹道至太子道東，經啟德下的暗渠流入前啟德機場跑道和觀塘間水道。<br />\n<br />\n黃大仙區以住宅為主，工業樓宇集中在新蒲崗工業區。"},{"pid":"64e1dfcccb7ca3cfbcf5432b85b08e2c063ac9f4","tid":688632,"uid":20430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T15:07:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/04/230753_17a750533fc65a3581aa8efe3d9d9fc4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F04%2F230753_17a750533fc65a3581aa8efe3d9d9fc4.png&h=b9f1786c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e43e5ed76024bef9f5b48aa5dc5cfd1ba04db2b8","tid":688632,"uid":126766,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T15:28:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a9fe2c1b982bc89fe73a729f6fc0efef9669816","tid":688632,"uid":14272,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"quote":{"pid":"e43e5ed76024bef9f5b48aa5dc5cfd1ba04db2b8","tid":688632,"uid":126766,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T15:28:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T15:38:10.000Z","msg":"大陸仔？冇住過？"},{"pid":"070ac63c5efb1c4ada4966cf640014919565d7b2","tid":688632,"uid":968,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T15:45:42.000Z","msg":"Siu4 得18區搞制縣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.g